ntentSub2\"></div>\n		\n		<div id=\"jump-to-nav\"></div>\n		<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#mw-head\">Jump to navigation</a>\n		<a class=\"mw-jump-link\" href=\"#searchInput\">Jump to search</a>\n		<div id=\"mw-content-text\" lang=\"en\" dir=\"ltr\" class=\"mw-content-ltr\"><div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><!-- ADDMETAK Q2xvdWQsIFNhYVMsIERvbGliYXJyLCBob3N0aW5nLCBzb2Z0d2FyZSwgc2VydmljZSwgaG9zdCwgcHJvdmlkZXIsIG9ubGluZSwgc2Z0cCwgcnN5bmM= -->\n</p><p><b>Dolibarr ERP &amp; CRM</b> is a software package designed to works as a standalone programm or as an application hosted into the Cloud. Having Dolibarr into the Cloud, is a solution to use Dolibarr from anywhere, any device, without doing any technical tasks (no installation to do, upgrades and backups are done for you).\n</p><p>This page try to list the main available services providing Dolibarr ERP &amp; CRM as a <b>SaaS or Cloud</b> solution. If you are looking for a partner for specific setup/development, see instead the <a href=\"/index.php?title=List_of_Dolibarr_partners_and_providers\" title=\"List of Dolibarr partners and providers\">List of Dolibarr partners and providers</a>.\n</p>\n<center>\n<p><a href=\"/index.php?title=File:Cloud_solutions.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Cloud solutions.png\" src=\"/images/7/7b/Cloud_solutions.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"350\" height=\"262\" data-file-width=\"350\" data-file-height=\"262\" /></a>\n</p>\n</center>\n<h2><span id=\"For_&quot;Ready_to_use&quot;_SaaS_commercial_solutions\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"For_.22Ready_to_use.22_SaaS_commercial_solutions\">For \"Ready to use\" SaaS commercial solutions</span></h2>\n<h3><span id=\"Recommended_(Dolibarr_Preferred_Partners)\"></span><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Recommended_.28Dolibarr_Preferred_Partners.29\">Recommended (Dolibarr Preferred Partners)</span></h3>\n<p><span class=\"opacitymedium\">Sort criterias are: 1) \"Automatic subscription\" (yes first, free trial without credit card first), 2) \"Age of offer\" (oldest first)</span>\n</p>\n<div class=\"company dolcompany\">\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"companytable\">\n<tbody><tr><td>\n<b>DoliCloud</b></td>\n<td align=\"right\">\n<div class=\"companylogo\"><a href=\"https://www.dolicloud.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\" noreferrer noopener\"><img alt=\"Dolicloud logo.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/8/8b/Dolicloud_logo.png/104px-Dolicloud_logo.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"104\" height=\"32\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/8/8b/Dolicloud_logo.png/156px-Dolicloud_logo.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/8/8b/Dolicloud_logo.png/208px-Dolicloud_logo.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"520\" data-file-height=\"160\" /></a></div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\">\n<div class=\"companytext small\">\n<ul><li>Use your ERP &amp; CRM from anywhere through an internet connection</li>\n<li>Opened hosting (you keep full access to your data/files, SSH, SFTP and Direct Mysql connection supported)</li>\n<li>Support in english and french (including help for migration)</li>\n<li>Daily data backup.</li>\n<li>Version upgrades included.</li>\n<li>Cancel your subscription at any time.</li></ul>\n<p><b>Create in 2 clicks your instance for a 15-day trial of the Dolibarr cloud-based application with free upgrades and support at <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://myaccount.dolicloud.com/register.php?origin=wikicloud&amp;utm_source=wikicloud&amp;utm_campaign=none&amp;utm_medium=web\">DoliCloud</a></b>\n</p><p>Or watch the tutorial to create your own instance: <a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hMNjvManaF4\" title=\"DoliCloud Video\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer noopener\"><img alt=\"DoliCloud Video\" src=\"/images/thumb/3/3d/Dolicloud_video.png/100px-Dolicloud_video.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"100\" height=\"56\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/3/3d/Dolicloud_video.png/150px-Dolicloud_video.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/3/3d/Dolicloud_video.png/200px-Dolicloud_video.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"1920\" data-file-height=\"1080\" /></a><br />\nWeb: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://www.dolicloud.com?origin=wikicloud&amp;utm_source=wikicloud&amp;utm_campaign=none&amp;utm_medium=web\">https://www.dolicloud.com</a><br />\nRegistration: <a target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://myaccount.dolicloud.com/register.php?origin=wikicloud&amp;utm_source=wikicloud&amp;utm_campaign=none&amp;utm_medium=web\">From this form</a>, instance ready in 30 seconds<br />\nCertified <a href=\"/index.php?title=File:Dolibarr_preferred_partner_int.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Dolibarr preferred partner int.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/9a/Dolibarr_preferred_partner_int.png/100px-Dolibarr_preferred_partner_int.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"100\" height=\"39\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/9a/Dolibarr_preferred_partner_int.png/150px-Dolibarr_preferred_partner_int.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/9/9a/Dolibarr_preferred_partner_int.png/200px-Dolibarr_preferred_partner_int.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"401\" data-file-height=\"158\" /></a><br />\n</p>\n</div></td></tr>\n</tbody></table>\n</div>\n<div class=\"company dolcompany\">\n<table width=\"100%\" class=\"companytable\">\n<tbody><tr><td>\n<b>NovaFirstCloud by Teclib</b></td>\n<td align=\"right\">\n<div class=\"companylogo\"><a href=\"https://www.novafirstcloud.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\" noreferrer noopener\"><img alt=\"NovaFirstcloud.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/9/98/NovaFirstcloud.png/94px-NovaFirstcloud.png\" decoding=\"async\" width=\"94\" height=\"32\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/9/98/NovaFirstcloud.png/140px-NovaFirstcloud.png 1.5x, /images/9/98/NovaFirstcloud.png 2x\" data-file-width=\"169\" data-file-height=\"58\" /></a></div>\n</td></tr>\n<tr><td colspan=\"2\">\n<div class=\"companytext small\">\n<ul><li>Use your ERP &amp; CRM from anywhere through an internet connection</li>\n<li>Support in english and french (including help for migration)</li>\n<li